page.title: 19MEDIA IN DELABOLE
page.content:
{"My favourite TV programme": children's survey results. Street Hawk had 10 votes. The A Team had 8 votes. The East-enders had 3 votes. Other programmes named included: Coronation Street, Grange Hill, Birdwatch,Knightrider,Play School, Dallas and Supergran.
{" My favourite book": children's survey results. The Bible had 6 votes. Alice in Wonderland. ) The Never-ending story.) had 3 each. Ghostbusters ) Three Little Pigs )had 2 each. The Faraway Tree ) Other books named included The Hobbit, Heidi,Carbonel,Famous Five,Gumdrop,The BFG,and the Guinness Book of Records.
